snippet.title: 🌗ANOTHEREAL Gameplay Trailer 🌓 [Project Astray]
snippet.description:
Announcing ANOTHEREAL, a new RPG by Lena Raine featuring shmup-style battles & an EXISTENCE system that changes how you interact with the world.

Wishlist now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2895500/ANOTHEREAL/

Or check out the info sheet for more details!
